  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK396">
<l>toṭṭaṉait tūṟu maṇaṟkēṇi māntarkkuk</l>
<l>kaṟṟaṉait tūṟumaṟivu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Water will flow from a well in the sand in proportion to the depth to which it is dug, and knowledge will flow from a man in proportion to his learning.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
